<div class="quick-step">
<div class="quick-num">4</div>
<div class="quick-content">
<div class="quick-action">Find the real Shift</div>
<div class="quick-desc">Not the comfortable answer. Arrive at it without announcing it. Stop when the change has landed.</div>
<div class="quick-time">~2 min</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="quick-step">
<div class="quick-num">5</div>
<div class="quick-content">
<div class="quick-action">Write the End</div>
<div class="quick-desc">One message. One final line strong enough to stand alone. Nothing after it.</div>
